text.tspan: People living in countries in which a woman is government's chief executive, World, 1800 to
The chief executive is the head of government or head of state, whoever has more power. This is recorded on December 31 of each year.
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13)
Note: V-Dem covers many more countries since 1900.
